            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國出口為經濟成長帶來1997年以來最大助力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 中國依靠出口推動經濟成長的程度已達到近三十年前亞洲金融危機以來未曾見過的水平，展現出的實力使其得以挺過美國總統特朗普發起的貿易戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家統計局局長康義周一在新聞發布會上表示，貨物和服務淨出口對去年經濟成長的貢獻率接近33%。這一比例較2024年的水平高出兩個百分點以上，也是自1997年以來的最高水平，當時該比例略高於42%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個全球第二大經濟體去年實現了政府設定的目標，全年經濟增速達5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-59011a26-9aeb-33b1-bbf0-8b476d86b86f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O4sa.04b5b4T2QwECHSVJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/60cc135ab62bcf380ea29374f1b3f67c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著中國受到特朗普最高達145%關稅的壓力時，其工廠紛紛將出口訂單從美國轉移至歐洲和東南亞等地區。製造商還通過增加高端產品的銷售，向價值鏈上游移動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對中國設備和機械的需求也受益於產業鏈出海。與此前預期的放緩趨勢相反，上個月出口出現回升，使中國的貿易順差達到創紀錄的1.2萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出口的顯著作用日益被視為一體兩面：既蘊含優勢，也伴隨風險。這反映出經濟的供需失衡日益加劇，而這也是政策制定者確定的2026年的一個關鍵挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著中國出口引擎持續強勁運轉，未來幾年中國面臨著保護主義加劇的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在國內消費和商業需求疲軟的背景下，近年來進口一直停滯不前。作為衡量投資活動的指標，去年，資本形成總額對經濟成長的貢獻率創下1997年以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Chinese Exports Give Biggest Growth Boost to Economy Since 1997</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%82%BA%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%861997%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%A9%E5%8A%9B-072041855.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-19 21:29:18",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛：美國最新關稅威脅對歐洲經濟衝擊料有限 其中德國恐受最大影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 高盛集團的經濟學家表示，美國總統特朗普對歐洲部分國家最新提出的10%關稅威脅可能會對歐元區國內生產毛額(GDP)構成約0.1%的拖累。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普周六表示，將對聲援格陵蘭的歐洲國家加徵關稅。相關措施將適用於丹麥、挪威、瑞典、法國、德國、芬蘭、英國和荷蘭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛團隊估計，10%的關稅將通過貿易的減少使上述受影響國家的實際GDP下降0.1%至0.2%。他們表示，德國面臨的衝擊將最大，如果是增量對等關稅，料對其GDP構成約0.2%的衝擊；如果是全面加徵，影響料為0.3%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0d1d44ff-26ce-39e7-8728-296814d27e95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果信心受挫或金融市場出現不利影響，衝擊可能更大，」包括Sven Jari Stehn在內的團隊在報告中寫道。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aDakZyFyEHC_zj8Cvv0sNQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8d1eb4c9a80c893606592d473dfbb96e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛經濟學家表示，關稅是否會真正落地仍「高度不確定」，而歐盟可能的回應包括：拖延與美國的貿易協議、加徵反制性關稅，或啟動所謂的「反脅迫工具」。高盛預計，英國將把重點放在與川普進行外交層面的接觸上，與去年貿易談判時的做法類似。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛經濟學家還認為，對通膨的影響「非常小」，並預計各國央行會根據GDP前景下調利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Economists See Limited US Tariff Hit to European Growth</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%B0%8D%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E6%96%99%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%81%90%E5%8F%97%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-113142602.html",
